snippet.title: Dumb Ways to Survive: Coming Soon
snippet.description:
Dumb Ways to Survive, a brand new survival roguelike game from the Dumb Ways to Die brand, COMING SOON to Netflix Games! 

Embark on a new adventure - collect, harvest and hunt your way through the wilderness as a bumbling Bean trying to stay alive. Will you die a dummy or use your smarts to survive?

---
About  @Netflix  
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with over 260 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
